<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span>郑报全媒体记者</span><span></span><span>谢鹏飞</span><span></span><span>通讯员</span><span></span><span>赵莎莎</span><span></span><span>魏诗桐</span><span></span><span>文</span><span>/</span><span>图</span></strong></p>
